2011;;The Girl in the White Coat;;Canadian;;Darrell Wasyk;;Pascale Monpetit;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Girl_in_the_White_Coat;;Elise, a factory worker who lives in isolation and is tormented by her co-workers, decides that despite her lack of money, she must get her coat fixed. A case of mistaken identity pulls her into events she had not intended.[2]